  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2019-06-05",
    "date": "2020-02-12T19:45:07Z",
    "text": "Saving Local News Act of 2019\n\nThis bill includes as a tax-exempt 501(c)(3) nonprofit purpose the publication (including electronic publication) of written news articles. Currently, a tax-exempt nonprofit purpose includes religious, charitable, scientific, and other purposes, as specified.\n\nIn the case of an organization that is tax-exempt due to the publication of written news articles, the term unrelated business taxable income does not include any amount attributable to payments for advertisements in news publications."
